images.title: An ancient glacial landscape
images.caption: Knuthöjdsmossen, a nature reserve in Sweden
images.desc: Discover Knuthöjdsmossen, a nature reserve that covers almost 250 acres near the city of Hällefors, Sweden. This tranquil haven features a boardwalk that meanders through a bog, showcasing several small lakes, sand dunes, marshes, and pines.
